mg width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Dn17O7VAvcbkfSTiaP2xMFAaTLVmI0CqNrJUzzobuJH2foFp4al9s0aLEsXCoCBfRowhAH9Lh5q5JjBmxWUnrKw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/Dn17O7VAvcbkfSTiaP2xMFAaTLVmI0CqNPKp62rlicKym0R82c5CSQ6ZhXicS7OYYLWPMdbfJSDwfrQ5TWMibibVZfQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;编辑留言&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#595959;&quot;&gt;怎么样，这个改造牛不牛，只要有想法，就能实现。&lt;span&gt;如果你刚好有房子需要装修，您可以来改造家咨询！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:normal;&quot;&gt;我们可以为你推荐设计师，我们的设计师擅长各种风格，保证能给你满意的设计方案，你根本不需要担心自己的房子如何设计，点击“&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FF4C00;&quot;&gt;阅读原文&lt;/span&gt;”报名吧！把这些头大的问题统统交给我们设计师吧。。而且是&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#FF4C00;line-height:normal;&quot;&gt;免费的！免费的！免费的！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;', '', '1', '1493017736', '/Uploads/1/image/2017-04-24/58fda48790fc9.jpg', '0');
INSERT INTO `gms_article` VALUES ('134', '104', '699元从毛坯到精装的华美蜕变，破茧成蝶！', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:2em;&quot;&gt;\r\n		交房后的毛坯房经大卫易轩签约设计师打造后，破茧成蝶，变成了精装小豪宅，小编今天来和大家分享一个参加699装修的案例，感觉美到不行\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#595959;&quot;&gt;位置：加州1885&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#595959;&quot;&gt;户型：两室一厅&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#595959;&quot;&gt;面积：98米&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#595959;&quot;&gt;设计风格：美式风格&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#595959;&quot;&gt;装修公司：大卫易轩&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#595959;&quot;&gt;套餐：699装修包&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#595959;&quot;&gt;第三方监管：改造家&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;有家网设计师&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体;line-height:20px;&quot;&gt;人有三六九等但是他们对家的目的是一样的，来找我们的人都只有一个目的那就是把家设计好。所以我们对待每一个客户都想要尽可能的满足他们的需求！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:inherit;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#5F9CEF;font-size:36px;&quot;&gt;4.17&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#999999;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;在这之前，装修工人已经把防臭地漏和防水安装完毕，今天卫生间的瓷砖还在铺贴中，但也将近完工。这些工作及材料都是包含在套餐里的。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:inherit;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;IMG_3874.JPG&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad5PXrZSoiaChYIqVSr6hsuE7ZzVfFj8QUwsejdAeacwGmicCeCyMIY7vVOsyl9gglm527ttrGs0TRyA/0?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:inherit;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;IMG_3875.JPG&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad5PXrZSoiaChYIqVSr6hsuE7greYfWLiaqlRuA8JP6BGMGglYibPDpm1mRP5U0YRBfibWUrO8OhAm5wGA/0?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:inherit;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#5F9CEF;font-size:36px;&quot;&gt;4.26&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#999999;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;瓷砖贴完后，大卫易轩装修工人将水电管道贴条标记，以防弄错，准备下一步做木工，装吊顶了。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;QQ图片20160427145059.jpg&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad6T4UHsSK3IuV0JLPolUYE1HGt1xmIKqa90HfTSiaHF8jTPsXyGQtwYUz2ZXviamEicZsVicJaicXbvKWQ/0?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;QQ图片20160427145120.jpg&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad6T4UHsSK3IuV0JLPolUYE1grmrjUTaAF57S6exxawwajC7OtltQd7iaNvZia81Xj51MicibMLGMfEPUA/0?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;QQ图片20160427145116.jpg&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad6T4UHsSK3IuV0JLPolUYE1GzRHjlxZpf972uxlegib7eHianiaWnjnev1bnXPSvwQT1vjeZia8Ov7gicQ/0?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;QQ图片20160427145054.jpg&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad6T4UHsSK3IuV0JLPolUYE10ZhN767CyehoNXMLwKZSvjRssNic0lY2Y3nHsSGNaqfktIYOicR1s9gQ/0?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:inherit;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#5F9CEF;font-size:36px;&quot;&gt;5.26&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#999999;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;吊顶装完后，感觉客厅一下子有了立体感，当然吊顶浴霸这些东西都是包含在套餐里的，没有任何附加费用。下一步工作&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;批腻子后乳胶漆涂刷。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;IMG_3401.JPG&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad4EA9SRXqFhY2BoEOMJ8KwkI843oXiapCkFnCfialZCaBkJnziaQuQrQ4h4PRkDgC9jOmxkDZoF0QeSA/0?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;img title=&quot;IMG_3391.JPG&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad4EA9SRXqFhY2BoEOMJ8KwknZ4sjofcGDkm0G9z0s2lmjKZy4VHKXTNLNbyWsVDxuDYcYV6Dx2nVA/0?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:inherit;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;color:#5F9CEF;font-size:36px;&quot;&gt;6.15&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#999999;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;color:#3E3E3E;line-height:22.4px;&quot;&gt;验收交房，又一个工地完工了，业主脸上的笑意是我们最大的收获，看着温馨的现场，觉得好满足。大家来看看装修完成后的效果吧！&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;p&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;IMG_2572.JPG&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad4XdqRriaGhNCR7BWUZEcJ0rraxs4S6EW7DjWgVWwX3DP2rgvJApuibLXrqK9SmC3ibkbxhxrwXdSEiaw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;IMG_2571.JPG&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad4XdqRriaGhNCR7BWUZEcJ0r6e4LJbFnqibiaNSO6WIFPRsGIjEqOXMX6IicaoksFInLwW4nL5C5oeN5A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;IMG_2567.JPG&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad4XdqRriaGhNCR7BWUZEcJ0rIux2ZoQsK03JYle3iaO2lg06kXIGBRArqhL7U3ibp9g2g0kO2I7FWPMA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;img title=&quot;IMG_4154.JPG&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad4sGrDqT1rPT8DvzicecNQoXSZe0wvXQtibIBSNPbP7oSFutuNPUAhEXrLP43FP0nhKPJQRibY37o5Qg/0?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;IMG_2568.JPG&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad4XdqRriaGhNCR7BWUZEcJ0rebibUHINIorxsOASZrfaI3RZtFsyLUhvI7vCHbrKljS86wCPfX5a9Jg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;img title=&quot;IMG_2570.JPG&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/G9VYr7Dwiad4XdqRriaGhNCR7BWUZEcJ0ruibZmfibGRl05SwxC9qm8iaXL9RUstk0o4dBD08sRTX1bkLFWaNehUBUQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;', '', '1', '1493018085', '/Uploads/1/image/2017-04-24/58fda5e25eff2.jpg', '0');
INSERT INTO `gms_article` VALUES ('135', '105', '140平土豪的家，刚进门就惊呆了！', '&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;户型：三室两厅&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;◆&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;面积：140平米&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;◆&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;风格：混搭风格+美式风格&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;有家网设计师&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span&gt;根据户型特点，我在这里设计了三个大小不一的弧形门洞，配上简单的造型，让空间显得通透大气。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:25.6px;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;家具精美的轮廓完美的勾勒出淳朴自然的美式风格， 不论是匠心独运的沙发，还是古色古香的储柜，都让客厅综合着硬朗的气质，诠释出复古的韵味&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;1000&quot; width=&quot;1330&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/k0UEYItqwJUqp9ss8OheBGKbwa08tBWMcpq8AiajEuyweXB8GZ1iamaho7azssJG6GmjeA79J7NQof6iaDjVuyMIg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;&quot;&gt;红色文化砖墙两边的白色高柜相互呼应，同时大大增加储物空间，旁边的绿植也让空间更加具有活力。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;1000&quot; width=&quot;1495&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/k0UEYItqwJUqp9ss8OheBGKbwa08tBWMRHJ7HpGIbLxMkCTEkWMXqhRB1GIwA5Ghb3h7hU2Y0ia2NmSzuPf8SIA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;line-height:1.75em;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;客厅书柜的正面照：在这里，客厅不再是看电视的地方，错落有致的格子储物柜取代了电视柜，让客厅成为了会友聊天的场所，累了躺在沙发上小憩一会儿，伴着花香做个美梦！&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;1000&quot; width=&quot;1217&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/k0UEYItqwJUqp9ss8OheBGKbwa08tBWMibD5knBctnuZGe2Xx3flPd4DvzxwPkTDF0ia0RD74UXOpDYoPwM7EoCw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;皮质沙发加上复古原木茶几的混搭组合，集粗犷，自由，休闲于一体！&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;1000&quot; width=&quot;1206&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/k0UEYItqwJUqp9ss8OheBGKbwa08tBWMpmiasto62cnnz8DQ7lnqUPicupqh3y1VGZjZyhOMDiajYeUZcPib3Moahw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;原木的餐桌椅在复古的吊扇灯的映射下显得格外温馨。白色线条对餐厅背景的简单分割，刷上淡灰色乳胶漆，再挂上一副抽象画，让整个用餐区域告别单调。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;1000&quot; width=&quot;1250&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/k0UEYItqwJUqp9ss8OheBGKbwa08tBWMOAJZlbQicaSIRRejSlQoibTJAwZ5ZPRJVkCVYktFF9KicB7WkEyQic9hbw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;1000&quot; width=&quot;1354&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/k0UEYItqwJUqp9ss8OheBGKbwa08tBWMHVxA8ZgPCKhnbKcNRPKpSa6y4taI43ueASfoqBs2dTTeSgzLkDzpoA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;color:#000000;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;实木的床，配套的床头柜，书桌，加上素色的窗帘，即使有印花的床上用品，也掩盖不了主人那颗质朴的心。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; height=&quot;1000&quot; width=&quot;1391&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/k0UEYItqwJ