t-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体, SimSun;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;▼家具都是精选矮矮小小的，个头不大，这样小空间看起来也不显局促。从配色到家具，每一处都体现了屋主的小心思。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体, SimSun;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/MIgEIG8lVzlWQKZ2ox6n8qqzJiaLsuzdbUTc9vnXBVMJlaO5ogiao803ZpEvAYwPRzGmlSoIZf9Bc2riboFJcUqJw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体, SimSun;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n		&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:宋体, SimSun;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;▼原本的画风是左侧这样的，有点不忍直视。屋主把玻璃移门拆了，增加空间的互动性，再对墙面进行美颜，便成了这清新脱俗的模样，感觉年轻了20岁。&lt;/span&gt; \r\n	&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:-apple-system-font, \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;