INSERT INTO `gms_article` VALUES ('155', '103', '我和老公的新房，越看越喜欢，尤其是我家的厨房！', '&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	房子面积不大，建筑面积84.58㎡，除去公摊+赠送面积，实际套内在70㎡左右。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	我们家的户型比较方正，3房朝南。但由于面积小，可变化性不高，我们想着在网上先看看有没有合适的装饰公司，于是找到了有家网这个大型的网上装修平台，我们在有家网上看到了大卫易轩装饰公司，不管从设计上还是施工上，让我和老公都很喜欢，由于我们比较忙，所以在装修期间一直都是大卫易轩的工作人员在忙前忙后，最终的效果我和老公还是比较喜欢的，现在让大家看看效果。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;进户门&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	进门的左手边做了柜子，可以放一些鞋子和小东西。中间做了隔断，可以放钥匙之类的随手小物品。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;text-align:center;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;auto&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/jqs2bxY3a1QWAhtLMkRDlNXHWmyXGicGp75dbjR5poTTEeD2fBDibYkfDhtmjRXX0Kib2D1ibG902Tubzjy8UnBv9w/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;amp;tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;餐厅&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	因为户型的原因，餐桌买了1米3配了4把椅子，都是在有家网上买的，质量还是OK的。叉背椅还是那么美啊。\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;img clas