4px;&quot;&gt;在厨房里摆上一瓶花，增添一些生气~装上白色的吊灯，每天晚上都是浪漫的烛光晚餐。&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/A3BricXFQia45nx1WE8qMn5FPvVtiaY0d6QVWIhMKbrOLib8sxRdBQQDog6rPjXibjlWWbER1JbZCicvWT2FiaV1W9rGQ/640?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/CCWic1qUpoDicJtRKSFtaRlb6DVw4r9HecDpfgQQr1n6U7eDMWic748VicrhmEFoVv3aRyvBCgpxp5gxDqhDatGjiag/640?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#17365D;&quot;&gt;5、浴 &amp;nbsp;室&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;亮堂堂的浴室，让你体验不一样的沐浴方式&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/A3BricXFQia45nx1WE8qMn5FPvVtiaY0d6QNe9fdzuopOytubVtRTeRvlssyFA1vP7kekkDJCH8u9ILlEHiaeOPqKA/640?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/A3BricXFQia45nx1WE8qMn5FPvVtiaY0d6Q69S2JcYde9huN2afJubdn0Pe7QmDOsyyDbrNkXiagRlTchY9H1IbL1g/640?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#17365D;&quot;&gt;6、阁楼 户外&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;这样的阁楼，就是午休憩息的好天地~你需要一把躺椅&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/CCWic1qUpoDicJtRKSFtaRlb6DVw4r9HecfeTsMY3hDsngQlYk8F7JHhxKu0dUOMQw2XP4lmsh8ZhDibvsm5thicnQ/640?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14px;&quot;&gt;户外也是当然也不能马虎，从进家门那一刻起，就幸福感爆棚。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;auto&quot; class=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/A3BricXFQia46YuVeicqiaKA4NwB89GcibVzIiaWMtOvjxRErBjHiafpKlpic0M77dy0hYLLVZN9HJ7XavDhTiaDn0xzaSw/640?tp=webp&amp;amp;wxfrom=5&amp;amp;wx_lazy=1&quot; style=&quot;height:auto !important;width:auto !important;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;', '', '1', '1498633547', '/Uploads/1/image/2017-06-28/59535247d6e27.jpg', '0');
